OL,3,CSenior Birmingham City councillor
OL,4,CWaseem Zaffar dies suddenly aged 44
OL,6,FA senior Birmingham City councillor,
OL,7,Fdescribed as a "passionate advocate of
OL,8,Fhis community", has died aged 44.
OL,10,FWaseem Zaffar represented the Lozells
OL,11,FWard from 2011 and served in several
OL,12,Fsenior cabinet roles on Birmingham
OL,13,FCity Council, including transport,
OL,14,Fenvironment, climate change and
OL,15,Fhighways.
OL,17,FHe was most notably involved in
OL,18,Fleading the development of the
OL,19,FBirmingham Clean Air Zone and was a
OL,20,Fpassionate advocate on environmental
OL,21,Fissues.
