OL,6,FReacting to his death on Friday night,
OL,7,Fthe leader of Birmingham City Council,
OL,8,FJohn Cotton, said: "It is so
OL,9,Fincredibly hard to put into words how
OL,10,FI and so many of my colleagues across
OL,11,Fthe City Council feel tonight.
OL,13,F"Waseem Zaffar was a passionate
OL,14,Fadvocate of his community, a father, a
OL,15,Fhusband, a young man with so much more
OL,16,Fto give to the city he was so proud to
OL,17,Fcall home.
