OL,6,F"Tonight, we remember a life lost too
OL,7,Fsoon, and a family that has suffered
OL,8,Fthe most terrible and shocking of
OL,9,Flosses. My thoughts and prayers are
OL,10,Fwith them all tonight and in the days
OL,11,Fto come."
OL,13,FWaseem's work touched many aspects of
OL,14,Fpublic life in the city, and tributes
OL,15,Ffrom colleagues and residents reflect
OL,16,Fthe breadth of his commitment to
OL,17,Fcommunity and public service.
